org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus

Interface ModbusBlock

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModbusBlockImpl

    public interface ModbusBlock
    A representation of the model object 'Block'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Block Type
    • Start Address
    • Count
    • Period
    • Timeout
    • Type

    See Also:
    ModbusPackage.getModbusBlock()
